{"tid":1321692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「借力打力」利用TVB霸權力量","createTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T17:41:58.000Z","uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2824e20da12992cd075e42640f9b70cdd0977fc4","tid":1321692,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:05.000Z","msg":"今日落公園執葉，聽到兩個廢青係道討論利用電視機youtube播放功能，仿製TVB新聞台。<br />\n「如其抵制TVB，倒不如利用TVB咁受藍絲歡迎既賣點，<br />\n弟兄係享天輪樂時，事先接上已被仿製的TVB新聞，予家中父母觀看，<br />\n<br />\n原影片<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3QQxAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3QQxAP.jpg&h=4da899cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仿製影片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5UMoSAS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5UMoSAS.jpg&h=43ed10a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多時藍絲睇TVB都係因為覺得佢係主流新聞台唔會衰得去邊，<br />\n抵制TVB好難，所以不如用TVB既力量感染呢班老人家。<br />\n操作上需求有剪片技術，將已FACT CHECK既影片剪輯成<br />\n(一套TVB新聞+平時TVB賣既廣告)*3 =大概45分鐘時間，<br />\n當新聞開始重復，以便有藉口由youtube模式，轉番成平時電視模式。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣老人家先有可能信接觸到既資訊。<br />\n<br />\n影片長達45分鐘(記住唔好較public)，<br />\n需要人士有:<span style=\"color: red;\"> 影片組，旁白組，字幕組</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n唔太熟法律野，真心求問，咁樣佢地有冇觸犯任何法例?"},{"pid":"5f69d3b48107e43fa40f575406c637547d10f18c","tid":1321692,"uid":95102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">唔好意思阻你少少位<br />\n我打咗份聲明俾721嘅義士宣讀<br />\n希望各位巴打可以入嚟幫手改下</div></span><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n=========================<br />\n<br />\n721衝之前應該要搵人開記者會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320570\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320570</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n========================="},{"pid":"dcad07ee082fc3ddbfc9bd4259acaf33d81010f8","tid":1321692,"uid":81273,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"又黎？<br />\n人地播愛回家三百萬人收視播滾動字幕睇即刻收你皮<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/NOW-STATEMENT-190613016.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FNOW-STATEMENT-190613016.jpg&h=5ebeaca0&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}